### Sportstensor Week 12 Update @sportstensor・41 
# :yipee: SN41 New Incentive Mechanism is Live on Mainnet
It is with great pleasure to announce the official launch of our updated incentive mechanism on mainnet!

We first announced the transition in Week 5 (for those following along at home!) and 7 weeks later, we poured extensive time and resources into our whitepaper, rewrote thousands of lines of code, migrated our repo, took on feedback from validators, ran on testnet, squashed some bugs thanks to miners who helped us test and now here we are.

## __Incentive Mechanism v2__ 
New GitHub repo: https://github.com/sportstensor/sportstensor

## :egirl: What is it?
SN41 incentivises the consistent discovery of edges over the closing line odds - This indicates that machine dominance over the entire sports betting industry is asserted by top miners of our subnet. :100: 
- Validators now request `GetLeagueCommitments` as well as `GetMatchPrediction`
- Miners can now **choose** which league to make predictions for through the `miner.env` file. e.g. `LEAGUE_COMMITMENTS=NFL,MLB,EPL`
- Leagues are weighted differently which affects miner incentive.
- Miner response now needs to include `probabilityChoice` and `probability`

## :headshake: Why is this important?
- Closing odds are the pinnacle of market efficiency (accuracy) set by the use of thousands of machine learning algorithms. 
- Even the sharpest lines correctly predicts single event outcomes only ~52% of the time.
- **We are creating true machine intelligence** by beating out all other algorithms. AI vs. AI! :thanosdaddy: 
- Even with this intelligence, it is extremely hard for bettors to be profitable when bookmakers heavily restrict winners. (Stickiness factor to our subnet)
- Huge demand for performant predictive AI by betting operators, firms, syndicates and algo traders.
- Attract ai/ml talent from different industries to apply their expertise in sports prediction markets. :yousmart: 

## :pepenotes: How do we do this?
- Scoring mechanism: https://github.com/sportstensor/sportstensor/blob/main/vali_utils/scoring_utils.py
- AI darwinism at its finest. :Swole_DOGE: 
- Pareto distribution that disproportionately rewards top models. Meritocracy.
- Rolling window for scoring smoothes out the occasional punishments for incorrect predictions. :dogesmile:
